h1. render partial if file exist

<c>
<%= render :partial => params[:controller]+"/sidebar" if File.exists?(RAILS_ROOT+"/app/views/"+params[:controller]+"/_sidebar.html.erb")%>
</c>

"source":http://seanbehan.com/programming/render-partial-if-file-exists/

h1. don't rails if  file doesn't exist

<c>
<%= render :partial => params[:provider] rescue nil %>
</c>

"source":http://seanbehan.com/programming/render-partial-if-file-exists/

